    public abstract class ChannelOutboundAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements emds.epi.decl.server.communicationengine.OutboundChannel
    Baseclass for a user defined outbound channel. As an implementor, one has to derive the own channel class from this base class. Please see the example channel how it will be used
